  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the sea bream under cold water and pat it dry with paper towels",
    "Cut the sea bream into thin sashimi slices",
    "Mix the lemon juice, olive oil, salt, black pepper, and grated ginger in a small bowl",
    "Arrange the sashimi slices on a plate and drizzle the lemon juice mixture over them",
    "Sprinkle the chopped chervil over the sashimi slices",
    "Serve the sashimi with wasabi paste on the side",
    "Garnish with additional chervil if desired"
